summary: Worked as part of a cross-functional and international team on Benefit Connect, a single-tenant B2B SaaS solution that powers the employee benefits experience for employers.
highlights: Administered the product release consumption process, coordinating with core product teams to integrate updates into client instances, improving reliability and security.
Revamped billing exports, improving accuracy and reliability to meet service level agreements (SLAs), reducing errors impacting client billing and employee benefits.
Developed a custom HSA match program, including a tool that enabled employees to determine company contributions based on their elections.
